1
00:00:35,100 --> 00:00:36,580
♪Knowing that duckweed and moss♪

2
00:00:36,580 --> 00:00:40,340
♪Vanish in the sweep of millennia♪

3
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:42,260
♪I beg a year's bloom and fade♪

4
00:00:42,260 --> 00:00:44,730
♪One life of love and hate, untouched♪

5
00:00:44,730 --> 00:00:45,780
♪By soil's embrace♪

6
00:00:45,780 --> 00:00:48,280
♪In the torrent's rush, wreckage remains♪

7
00:00:48,280 --> 00:00:49,760
♪Knowing we sink in dust♪

8
00:00:49,760 --> 00:00:53,800
♪Still I stand by your side, unafraid♪

9
00:00:53,950 --> 00:00:56,320
♪Storms drench the city.
Blood stains our shade♪

10
00:00:56,320 --> 00:01:00,460
♪I'm not afraid the world
turns into our foe♪

11
00:01:02,150 --> 00:01:03,060
♪As I turn my gaze♪

12
00:01:03,060 --> 00:01:07,150
♪You arrive, holding an umbrella, as always♪

13
00:01:12,180 --> 00:01:16,100
=Born To Die=

14
00:01:16,140 --> 00:01:19,100
=Episode 22=

15
00:01:20,150 --> 00:01:21,480
If I meant nothing to you,

16
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:26,280
why didn't you kill me back then?

17
00:01:27,870 --> 00:01:29,200
If you didn't like me,

18
00:01:30,710 --> 00:01:32,480
why did you keep me by your side?

19
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:35,430
If you didn't love me,

20
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:37,710
why did you cry for me?

21
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:50,040
People in Nanlu see me
as their mortal enemy,

22
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,480
and everyone in the court

23
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:52,870
is keeping their eyes on me.

24
00:01:53,950 --> 00:01:55,580
If you marry me, once wars break out

25
00:01:55,580 --> 00:01:57,070
you'll be an enemy of both nations,

26
00:01:57,070 --> 00:01:58,230
with no way to turn back.

27
00:01:58,230 --> 00:01:59,950
Even if I must stand against the world,

28
00:02:00,150 --> 00:02:01,680
I will stay by your side.

29
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,840
In this life,

30
00:02:04,870 --> 00:02:06,560
if you wish to wander the world,

31
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,560
I will accompany you.

32
00:02:11,430 --> 00:02:13,240
If you aspire to conquer the realm,

33
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,680
I will support you.

34
00:02:18,290 --> 00:02:19,960
If you choose to resist til death,

35
00:02:21,980 --> 00:02:23,840
I will put my life on following you.

36
00:02:37,460 --> 00:02:38,730
In life, we share the same bed;

37
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:41,030
in death, the same tomb.

38
00:02:42,030 --> 00:02:43,400
Whether you are a general,

39
00:02:43,590 --> 00:02:44,960
an ordinary citizen,

40
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,470
or a fugitive,

41
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:49,750
the only person I will ever love

42
00:02:51,310 --> 00:02:52,960
is you, Song Dianxin.

43
00:02:55,470 --> 00:02:56,520
Song Dianxin,

44
00:02:59,750 --> 00:03:01,310
will you marry me?

45
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:37,180
♪Knowing we're mayflies♪

46
00:03:37,180 --> 00:03:41,210
♪Insignificant in vast cosmos♪

47
00:03:41,490 --> 00:03:43,880
♪I never knew your heart, let alone love♪

48
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:46,480
♪Time gently brushed them away♪

49
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:48,930
♪Outside the gates
of my heart, who lingers♪

50
00:03:48,930 --> 00:03:50,320
♪Facing flames and blade♪

51
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:54,290
♪I still can't hold you in my arms♪

52
00:03:54,570 --> 00:03:56,500
♪One glance leaves all silent♪

53
00:03:56,500 --> 00:04:01,080
♪Doomed eternally,
I still seek a moment of relief♪

54
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:05,240
♪Frost and snow leave no trace♪

55
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:07,910
♪Blank space remains♪

56
00:04:08,610 --> 00:04:10,090
♪Knowing that duckweed and moss♪

57
